              <span class="key-number">4</span>
              <h4>Feedback Loops</h4>
              <p>
                Some spirals stabilize. Others accelerate. The difference between a recession
                and a dark age is which kind of feedback dominates when the stress hits.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="key-card">
              <span class="key-number">5</span>
              <h4>Emergent Properties</h4>
              <p>
