          <div class="cascade-section">
            <div class="cascade-step">
              <div class="cascade-number">1</div>
              <div>
                <div class="cascade-title">The Optimization Trap</div>
                <div class="cascade-desc">Everything gets more efficient. Redundancy is eliminated. Supply chains tighten. The system has never worked better — and has never been more fragile.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cascade-step">
              <div class="cascade-number">2</div>
              <div>
                <div class="cascade-title">Warning Signs Dismissed</div>
                <div class="cascade-desc">Small failures occur. Isolated incidents, they're called. A pattern recognition specialist sees the connections. Nobody listens. They never do.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cascade-step">
              <div class="cascade-number">3</div>
              <div>
                <div class="cascade-title">The First Domino</div>
