            <div class="cascade-step">
              <div class="cascade-number">4</div>
              <div>
                <div class="cascade-title">Positive Feedback</div>
                <div class="cascade-desc">The collapse accelerates itself. Refugees spread chaos. Trade routes sever. Each failure triggers the next. The spiral becomes self-sustaining.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cascade-step">
              <div class="cascade-number">5</div>
              <div>
                <div class="cascade-title">The Threshold</div>
                <div class="cascade-desc">The point of no return. Even if the original trigger is resolved, the cascade continues under its own momentum. After this, there is no recovery — only survival.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cascade-step">
              <div class="cascade-number">6</div>
              <div>
                <div class="cascade-title">Selection</div>
                <div class="cascade-desc">Massive death. Knowledge loss. The Order's prepared bloodlines retreat to safe zones. The defensive network's carriers attempt to preserve what they can.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cascade-step">
              <div class="cascade-number">7</div>
              <div>
                <div class="cascade-title">Reset</div>
                <div class="cascade-desc">Survivors rebuild at lower complexity. Two hundred to five hundred years later, the cycle begins again.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

